Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這份真情實感　好想將它傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不沉溺於一去不返的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷於那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方應該有什麼正等待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝著那未完結的故事　飛奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷著一顆真誠的心向著那千難萬險之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}張開心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循環傳遞著一個訊息　幸福就存於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下來的少許勇氣　儘管須以眼淚相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但這或許正是變強的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溫暖的迭句　想要永遠將這份珍重守護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心緒交織　感受著這其中的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以說沒有人是孤身隻影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片藍天下　好想將這份真情實感傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷揣著內心深處收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}躍入未知的前方　那裡有什麼正等待著我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是與未來共鳴　不斷憶起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就會生出勇氣　就能變得堅強　也就不再是獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（讓你傾聽）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定會與你相遇　我會帶著真誠的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接夢想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}與其坐擁這無限的時刻　倒不如追趕那絢爛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　總有一天會讓你傾聽那夢中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  千秋啊  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  熊田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便坐吧  正好找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先借下體溫計嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有些發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天嘛  天氣又暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還是那麼隨便的下結論
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  我有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於千秋你們班主任田中老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看看  我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36度9  是不是該休息下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫度不高就算了  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看錯了  是37度1啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確點兒是37度1分9厘  休息5分鐘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就稍微休息會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  田中老師怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  田中老師挺優秀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健老師熊田剛好湊巧  目前正好沒男朋友哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能這麼告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠腹黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要檸檬汽水糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  總覺得很可怕  免了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  我覺得有點累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  貌似沒發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  拿著  以防萬一給你點兒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊  舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  下午的課要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是檸檬汽水糖嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  不過是精神疲勞罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會麻煩你負責救護了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:41.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第12碗  一口也吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近回來得很晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在做什麼可疑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當上運動會的負責人  有不少事要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道還能有別的什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你負責什麼呢  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責救護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊  為什麼這個時候開運動會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的小學還真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會真令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快點兒回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少動嘴多動手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是回去晚點兒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用扔下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是誰害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你討厭他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,態度太冷淡了吧  明明是鄰居
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家也不一起走…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為偶然住在隔壁  就必須一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備  跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夏奈叫來的  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在為運動會做特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別歇著了  特訓還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？還來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  不經過努力又何來勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在運動會這華麗的舞台上取得好成績  就只有特訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  教練
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你要不要一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要陪你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐她們好像玩得很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是犯傻罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說什麼就快說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學  是個有趣的運動會就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛突然說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個拐彎抹角的傢伙  搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這些也能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨能停就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣預報說會放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天聽說  隔壁那家又要搬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁  有些漫畫我還沒看過  現在去借
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁他們打包之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…明天再去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜  實在是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個多好的傢伙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得親近起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  還有這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼慣著她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木負責折紙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬負責把紙展開成花的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責綁線去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些我來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起來很快就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少動嘴多動手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  雖然現在說晚了點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆都姓「南」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我冬馬就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  叫我千秋就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女生！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起  冬馬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫法也很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備  跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  快衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～運動會加上隔壁鄰居搬家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們家事還真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:10:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是春天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得跟季節無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有個傢伙什麼季節都很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香你也參加什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有家屬也能參加的比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢  我得問問千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼悠閒自在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  南春香要參加運動會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想千秋一定很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得去參加社團活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～今天好豐盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為明天是運動會了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會去給你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話  在運動會上加油可是家人的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人聚在一起加油  運動會才熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人聚在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望明天能放晴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始舉行運動會開幕式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐就交給我了  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡…為什麼你會？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好嘛  和我們一起加油吧  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是第五個比賽項目  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年級學生的百米賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她們要參加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  內田  吉野  讓大家看看特訓的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位  預備…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己搞定  一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加借物跑的五年級學生  請馬上集合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼帶著夏奈跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個  因為沒別的合適人選了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  為什麼拉著藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在夠爆笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡是父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是父親？明明只有國二啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是各班代表參加的化裝遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班的代表是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和穿女裝的阿真好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡  上午的比賽項目全部結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去教室裡吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人沒有來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼也沒做  別第一個就下手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你加油也是很耗能量的啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木也別客氣  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次跟這麼多人一起吃便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃點兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點兒吃就沒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  下午有項目需要家屬參加  你怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？有那樣的項目嗎  我怎麼沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒打算讓你去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是讓春香參加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了  我也想參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是參加過了嗎  借物跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想參加別的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我再陪你參加一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何如何  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和南同學…是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我為今天而準備的…最強的手製義大利麵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水溫也必須達到最佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一份那不勒斯風味的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午的比賽馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請同學們各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是第二十七個比賽項目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年級學生與爸爸或媽媽的兩人三腳賽跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位  預備…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼緊張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會到這裡就正式閉幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有沒有義式黑胡椒麵了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義式香辣麵還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一會再收拾不也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別抱怨了  快點兒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊…為什麼冬木不待到最後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他硬是要參加上午的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都來了就待到最後嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說什麼就直說啊  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷  春天還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大早上起來就那麼多廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷就是冷  怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說廢話也不會暖和起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回來做點熱乎的東西當點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午沒課
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有春香沒課太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定今天上完上午的課就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！別無視我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  交換留學生已經決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我打算讓南同學去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都沒跟我們說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什麼內情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送別會要辦得盛大一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  來得正好  快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙…騙人的吧  我都沒聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家常的醋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在洗衣服時也有大用處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微倒入一點兒來代替柔順劑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服就會變得很柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不會留下醋味  可以放心使用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對防止面料退色也很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因衣服質地不同也會有不適用的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請事先調查好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:54.73,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(250,0)}第十三碗  「大家在一起、承蒙款待」
